她要带着婴儿护栏去华纳兄弟了  不回来了
She's taking her playpen to Warner Bros. Permanently.

1405
01:18:02,350 --> 01:18:03,400
华纳兄弟
Warner's?

1406
01:18:03,670 --> 01:18:05,620
我可不会让她出演玛丽·安托瓦内特
I wouldn't let her do Marie Antoinette.

1407
01:18:05,930 --> 01:18:07,550
高德温算是说对了一次
Goldwyn's right for once.

1408
01:18:07,550 --> 01:18:10,070
"扮演那个角色的喜剧演员就是要发笑"
"A comedienne in that role is to laugh."

1409
01:18:10,850 --> 01:18:13,890
而且她的片子十年来一分钱也没赚到
Besides, her pictures haven't made a dime in a decade.

1410
01:18:14,710 --> 01:18:16,760
恭喜  欧文
Congratulations, Irving.

1411
01:18:17,780 --> 01:18:19,320
我知道我的身份  曼克
I know what I am, Mank.

1412
01:18:19,880 --> 01:18:22,150
我不把工作当成体验生活
When I come to work, I don't consider it slumming.

1413
01:18:22,150 --> 01:18:24,750
我不用幽默来让自己显得超然物外
I don't use humor to keep myself above the fray.

1414
01:18:24,750 --> 01:18:26,990
并且我会为我的信念奋战到底
And I go to the mat for what I believe in.

1415
01:18:26,990 --> 01:18:30,260
我也没有时间搞别的
I haven't the time to do otherwise.

1416
01:18:30,880 --> 01:18:32,160
但你  先生
But you, sir,

1417
01:18:32,890 --> 01:18:34,340
像你这样的人
how formidable people like you

1418
01:18:34,340 --> 01:18:36,950
如果努力的话其实可以大有作为
might be if they actually gave at the office.

1419
01:18:38,740 --> 01:18:39,760
关上门
Close the door.

1420
01:18:57,580 --> 01:18:59,840
这张拍得真漂亮
Oh, that's a beautiful shot right there.

1421
01:19:25,040 --> 01:19:27,790
曼克  你还好吗
Mank! Are you okay?

1422
01:19:27,920 --> 01:19:31,050
不好  差点跑死我  威利在哪
No, that almost killed me. Where's Willie?

1423
01:19:31,280 --> 01:19:32,500
大概在开罗
Cairo, I think.

1424
01:19:32,500 --> 01:19:35,850
-你能给他打电话吗  -我从不给他打电话  都是他打给我
- Can you phone him? - I don't phone him, he phones me.

1425
01:19:35,850 --> 01:19:37,030
他什么时候回来
When's he due back?

1426
01:19:37,030 --> 01:19:40,460
11月6日之后吧  下周我去欧洲找他
After November 6th. I'm joining him in Europe next week.

1427
01:19:42,030 --> 01:19:45,730
