Marion, I need a favor. It's just a little joke on Willie.

1428
01:19:45,730 --> 01:19:46,700
当然  曼克  什么都行
Sure, Mank, anything.

1429
01:19:46,700 --> 01:19:49,750
我希望你回去跟梅耶说
I want you to go back and tell Mayer

1430
01:19:49,750 --> 01:19:54,050
什么辛克莱的虚假影片
Willie wants the phony Sinclair films pulled.

1431
01:19:55,940 --> 01:19:57,950
哪一部辛克莱假影片
Which phony Sinclair films?

1432
01:19:57,950 --> 01:20:01,160
