1447
01:21:20,150 --> 01:21:22,830
孤独的歌舞女郎  困在城堡里玩拼图游戏
The lonely showgirl, trapped in a castle, doing jigsaw puzzles.

1448
01:21:22,830 --> 01:21:27,620
那更像是不认识她的人对她的想象
It's more, her as people who don't know her imagine her to be.

1449
01:21:27,620 --> 01:21:28,660
