- I have to think about it. - Why?

1461
01:22:09,490 --> 01:22:12,430
因为我还不能确定她会怎么反应
'Cause I haven't made up my mind how she might react.

1462
01:22:12,480 --> 01:22:14,170
你的直觉呢
What does instinct tell you?

1463
01:22:14,170 --> 01:22:15,790
这是一剂强效药
It's mighty strong medicine

1464
01:22:15,790 --> 01:22:18,420
