He took the script?

1468
01:22:35,640 --> 01:22:37,030
他会给她看吗
Will he show it to her?

1469
01:22:39,930 --> 01:22:41,160
我不知道
I don't know.

1470
01:22:42,300 --> 01:22:43,550
你希望他给她看吗
Do you want him to?

1471
01:22:46,010 --> 01:22:47,160
我不知道
I don't know.

