01:44:07,890 --> 01:44:10,800
自从谢利·梅特卡夫的葬礼后  我就没见过你
Well, I haven't seen you since Shelly Metcalf's.

1754
01:44:11,380 --> 01:44:12,470
有那么久吗
Has it been that long?

1755
01:44:14,380 --> 01:44:15,750
最近如何  曼克
How you been, Mank?

1756
01:44:15,880 --> 01:44:17,300
